{"tid":1967840,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《老友記》延期開拍 宣佈趕不及下月出街","createTime":"2020-04-11T08:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T08:12:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d6d94bde9b834db39acf9f3d09bc23ae9c6e97a0","tid":1967840,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"經典喜劇的《老友記》（Friends）去年九月踏入25周年，早前大肆宣佈劇中六位主角將會世紀合體，配合新串流平台HBO Max的啟動，拍攝一小時的無劇本特備節目，並將於五月出街。不過，受到武漢肺炎疫情的影響，早前決定延期開拍的節目昨日證實趕不及於五月播出，節目原定於三月尾開始拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n雖然近期有不少節目都利用視訊科技，遠距離進行拍攝工作，但有指《老友記》就未有考慮跟風，因為節目要在劇集的原裝廠景拍攝才有意義。然而，全十季的《老友記》劇集將會如期在HBO Max推出時上架。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200411/large/1586581809_eec6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200411%2Flarge%2F1586581809_eec6.jpg&h=6c7289c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200411/3I2AST6F5OMRS3T5OVEUEFUNCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200411%2F3I2AST6F5OMRS3T5OVEUEFUNCQ%2F&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=86811afd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200411%2F3I2AST6F5OMRS3T5OVEUEFUNCQ%2F&h=6902e067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200411/3I2AST6F5OMRS3T5OVEUEFUNCQ/</a>"}]}